{
  "id": 3717,
  "name": "Draff",
  "desc": "<p>Draff Kätzlein is the head hunter for the village of Springvale. He is the father of Diona, a distant descendant of Olaf and part of the Kätzlein Bloodline. While he is a capable hunter and leader, he is also an alcoholic and a known member of the Four Drunkards. He will sell various meats during the day.</p>",
